<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Docker-Compose on Svtter's Blog</title><link>https://svtter.cn/tags/docker-compose/</link><description>Recent content in Docker-Compose on Svtter's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 17:14:55 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://svtter.cn/tags/docker-compose/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Coolify 和 Traefic 结合使用</title><link>https://svtter.cn/p/coolify-%E5%92%8C-traefic-%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 17:14:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://svtter.cn/p/coolify-%E5%92%8C-traefic-%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我使用 coolify 来管理多台服务器；但是 coolify 域名管理有点让人迷惑，我一直没能搞定。今天测试了一下，终于搞明白了。&lt;/p&gt;
